Summary: Very bright large light moving very fast.
divs: sighting detailswalking in from hunting, up to my right a very fast moving large bright light shot past. completely silent, not very high either, and seemed to burn out. very odd. lots of planes in the sky at the time to compare this to. it was definitely noy a plane or any other man made object. not to say it couldn't have been an asteroid\comet. i reported it to the local police. they had heard nothing...other than this was the day we crashed two probes into the moon. that isn't what i saw...very weird.
trends: There have been no other sightings in East Troy
